http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/power-shutdown/article13992850.ece

Power supply to some city areas will be hit on Monday. The areas that will be affected and the timings of power regulation are the following: areas between Thannikal and Perandoor near Edapally, Paadam, and Punnakkal: between 10.30 and 5.30 p.m.; Kalappurakkal and Kozhkoodu areas near Palluruthy: between 9 a.m. and 6 p.m.; Mulamthuruthy Pallithazam near Chottanikkara, Perumpilli, Kureekad, Kaniyavalli, Namboorichan Mala, Kambivelikkakam: between 9 a.m. and 5 p.m.; Kizhakkekkotta near Tripunithura, police station premises, Labham Market new bus stand, Guest House: between 10 am and 2 p.m.; Kannikad, Chilavannur, Kundannoor Temple, Martinpuram, Thomaspuram, Chambakkara, Nettoor north, Kannath Temple, Koothunkal: between 10 am and 5 p.m.